# the act of crossing an international border, generally for a very short period of time, in order to [[renew]] a [[visa]] or other government-issued permit before crossing back
#: {{ux|fr|Je dois '''faire le tour du poteau''' d'ici mai afin de renouveler mon permis de travail.|I need to '''cross the border''' between now and May in order to renew my work permit.}}
